headline: One Stop Systems (OSS) Soars 10.5%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?

headline: BofA upgrades Rockwell to Buy amid US industrial reshoring
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America upgraded Rockwell Automation (NYSE:ROK) to Buy from Neutral given early signs of operational improvement, cost-saving potential, and exposure to U.S. industrial reshoring as reasons for earnings upside over the next two years.
